  -ptabtools-0.3.1-r2.ebuild, ptabtools-0.4.3.ebuild:
  sparc stable wrt #200137, remove old

  24 Nov 2007; Dawid Węgliński <cla@gentoo.org> ptabtools-0.4.3.ebuild:
  Stable on x86 (bug #200137)

  28 Jul 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> ptabtools-0.4.3.ebuild:
  Use multilib.

*ptabtools-0.4.3 (28 Jul 2007)

  28 Jul 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> +ptabtools-0.4.3.ebuild:
  Version bump for bug 134256, thanks to Dominique Michel for reporting.

  19 Jun 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org>
  ptabtools-0.3.1-r2.ebuild:
  Added ~amd64

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  29 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ptabtools-0.3.1.ebuild,
  ptabtools-0.3.1-r2.ebuild:
  Add missing glib and pkgconfig dependencies, thanks to Sagar Mittal in bug
  #142602.

*ptabtools-0.3.1-r2 (15 Mar 2006)

  15 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  files/ptabtools-0.3.1-fPIC.patch,
  +files/ptabtools-0.3.1-respectflags.patch,
  +files/ptabtools-0.3.1-soname.patch, -ptabtools-0.3.1-r1.ebuild,
  +ptabtools-0.3.1-r2.ebuild:
  New version, this time respecting CFLAGS, LDFLAGS, CC, handling PIC
  correctly (it can build on amd64), multilib safe, and setting a soname on
  the shared library. Also fixed missing pkgconfig dependency.

  08 Jan 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove retiring dev from metadata.

*ptabtools-0.3.1-r1 (20 Feb 2005)

  20 Feb 2005; Patrick Dawson <pkdawson@gentoo.org>
  +files/ptabtools-0.3.1-fPIC.patch, +ptabtools-0.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed a few problems, made library build with -fPIC.
  Closes bug #81955. Thanks to Yaakov S.

  18 Dec 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  ptabtools-0.3.1.ebuild:
  Stable sparc, x86.

  04 Dec 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  ptabtools-0.3.1.ebuild:
  Added to ~sparc.

  17 Oct 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> ptabtools-0.3.1.ebuild:
